***BACK ON MARKET---NO FAULT OF SELLERS*** CHECK OUT THE 3D TOUR***ENJOY LOTS OF ROOM IN THIS WONDERFUL FRONT TO BACK SPLIT IN BEAUTIFUL OAK GROVE CLOSE TO FRICK PARK AND SOCCER FIELDS. 
New windows installed in every room except the front room and bathroom in 2023.
New Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring installed in kitchen, all bathrooms, laundry room, entry ways in 2023.
New aluminum railing and composite stairs installed on the front porch in September 2022.
New sliding glass door installed in 2022.
New roof, gutters, downspouts, and gutter screens installed in November, 2021. 
New dishwasher in 2023. 
New stove in 2022
New microwave in 2021
New air conditioner, furnace and tankless water heater installed in 2014.
Additional insulation added to attic in 2014.
